notes.title: Ethics approval
notes.p: The study was conducted according in compliance to the Animal Utilisation Protocol approved by the Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) of Universiti Putra Malaysia (Approval code: UPM/IACUC/AUP-R064/2016). The animals involved in this study were purchased and used solely in this study. The sampling from experiment animals were conducted under veterinary supervision.
